OL,3,CBus services face 'severe disruption'
OL,4,Cas Stagecoach drivers vote to strike
OL,6,FBus services in the North East face
OL,7,F"severe disruption" after Stagecoach
OL,8,Fworkers voted to strike over pay.
OL,10,FAction scheduled for Monday 18 August
OL,11,Fand Thursday 21 August was initially
OL,12,Fpostponed as members of Unite the
OL,13,FUnion were consulted on an offer to
OL,14,Fincrease pay by 5% over two years.
OL,16,FIt has since been rejected by 600
OL,17,Fworkers, meaning the strike will now
OL,18,Fgo ahead. Unite say the offer does not
OL,19,Foffer workers the same level of pay as
OL,20,Fcolleagues working in the North West.
