OL,3,CBus services face 'severe disruption'
OL,4,Cas Stagecoach drivers vote to strike
OL,6,FUnite regional officer Dave Telford
OL,7,Fsaid: "There will be severe disruption
OL,8,Fto bus services across Newcastle and
OL,9,FTyne and Wear but this is entirely the
OL,10,Ffault of Stagecoach for failing to put
OL,11,Fforward an acceptable offer.
OL,13,F"There is still time for industrial
OL,14,Faction to be avoided but that will
OL,15,Frequire Stagecoach tabling a deal its
OL,16,Fworkers can accept."
