OL,3,CBus services face 'severe disruption'
OL,4,Cas Stagecoach drivers vote to strike
OL,6,FIt will mainly affect services in
OL,7,FNewcastle, where drivers and engineers
OL,8,Fhave voted to strike. Engineers at the
OL,9,Fdepots in South Shields and Sunderland
OL,10,Fhave also opted for industrial action.
OL,12,FUnite have added that strike action
OL,13,Fwould intensify if the dispute was not
OL,14,Fresolved.
OL,16,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,17,Fsaid the latest offer "undervalued"
OL,18,FStagecoach workers.
