OL,6,FShe added: "Stagecoach is a profitable
OL,7,Fcompany and can afford to improve the
OL,8,Fdeal. The workers will receive Unite's
OL,9,Ffull backing during these pay strikes."
OL,11,FStagecoach have said there will be a
OL,12,Freduced service in Newcastle over the
OL,13,Ftwo days with passengers urged to plan
OL,14,Ftheir journeys in advance.
