OL,3,CBus services face 'severe disruption'
OL,4,Cas Stagecoach drivers vote to strike
OL,6,FSteve Walker, managing director of
OL,7,FStagecoach North East, said: "We are
OL,8,Fdisappointed that our latest offer
OL,9,Fincreasing the drivers' pay by 5% over
OL,10,Fthe course of the year has been
OL,11,Frejected by drivers and engineers at
OL,12,Four two Newcastle depots and by
OL,13,Fengineers at our Sunderland and South
OL,14,FShields depots.
