OL,4,Cas Stagecoach drivers vote to strike
OL,6,F"Our proposal was above inflation, and
OL,7,Fmet the Unions aspiration that the
OL,8,Ffinal rate was 5% higher. Newcastle
OL,9,Fdrivers are already the highest paid
OL,10,Fin the region compared to other large
OL,11,Foperators and have been awarded pay
OL,12,Frises in previous years that were well
OL,13,Fabove inflation.
