OL,3,CBus services face 'severe disruption'
OL,4,Cas Stagecoach drivers vote to strike
OL,6,F"It is also worth reiterating that
OL,7,Ftheir current demands would see
OL,8,Fadditional costs passed onto
OL,9,Fcustomers. Stagecoach buses are one of
OL,10,Fthe most cost-effective, accessible
OL,11,Fand convenient ways to travel around
OL,12,Fthe city, so this is something that we
OL,13,Fare absolutely keen to keep to a
OL,14,Fminimum.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
