OL,6,F"We remain committed to ensuring that
OL,7,Fdrivers do receive an affordable pay
OL,8,Fincrease. This strike action will
OL,9,Fcause unnecessary disruption across
OL,10,Four Newcastle-based communities, and
OL,11,Fwe urge the trade union members and
OL,12,FUnite the Union to reconsider their
OL,13,Fposition.
