OL,6,F"We will do everything possible to
OL,7,Fminimise the impact of the planned
OL,8,Findustrial action, but there will be a
OL,9,Freduced bus service across Newcastle
OL,10,Fon Monday 18 and Thursday 21 August.
OL,11,FAll other services in the North East
OL,12,Fand Tees Valley regions will continue
OL,13,Fto operate as normal.
OL,15,F"All service information will be
OL,16,Favailable on the Stagecoach app."
